        <!-- <h3 id="post-it-title">About the app</h3> -->
        <h3>How does this app work?</h3>
        <p class="font-italic little-text">Created by <strong>Memo</strong></p>
        <p class="px-1 d-inline little-text-border">ACTIVE FOR 1 DAY</p>
        <!-- <p><em>"Finally an app that allows you to get immediate feedback on any dilemma you're indecisive about. Engage with other users by voting, commenting or simply observing relatable dilemmas that others are facing. No dilemma is too small or big when we gather as a community to help each other decide."</em></p> -->
        <p id="main-paragraph">A few guidelines to help you navigate the app. Dilemmas are categorized by complexity, which the user selects when creating a dilemma.</p>
        <p id="second-paragraph">Once archived, only the creator of the dilemma can view the dilemma in their profile page.</p>
        <p id="third-paragraph">Each dilemma allows you to vote or comment. You can upvote other comments as well. So post your first dilemma or start voting now!</p>
      </div>
    </div>
</div>

